<li><em>Heads, VPs, Managers and Directors at Hospitals and Healthcare Networks in the areas of:</em>
<ul>
<li>Information &amp; Technology</li>
<li>Data Science, Engineering and Research</li>
<li>Innovation &amp; Transformation</li>
<li>Artificial Intelligence &amp; Machine Learning</li>
</ul>
</li>
