<p>In this episode no. 59 of Dream Big Podcast <strong>:</strong></p>
<p>Guest Ray Kurzweil explores what it&#8217;s like to be an inventor, how he gets inspiration for his projects &amp; ideas &#8212; plus a little on the clever super-heroine of his novel who achieves amazing things through the power of creative thinking.</p>
<hr class="dotted" />
<p><img style=' float: left; padding: 4px; margin: 0 7px 2px 0;'  class="alignleft  wp-image-306910 " title="digest - everyday kids - A3" src="http://www.kurzweilai.net/images/digest-everyday-kids-A3.png" alt="" width="577" height="381" /></p>
